xbrli:xbrl.in-capmkt:TopicsOrPrinciplesCoveredUnder:
Executive Directors
1. ESG Familiarisation Programme covering Global Sustainability Landscape, Business Responsibility & Sustainability Report, Reasonable Assurance and related updates
2. Code of Conduct
3. Anti-Bribery Management System
4. Cybersecurity Awareness
5. Creating a Respectful Workplace (POSHA)
6. Reliance Management System

Independent Directors and Non-Executive Directors
1. ESG Familiarisation Programme covering Global Sustainability Landscape, Business Responsibility & Sustainability Report, Reasonable Assurance and related updates
2. Code of Conduct
3. Familiarisation Programmes on:
a. Regulatory changes and their impact;
b. Compliance management framework;
c. Corporate Social Responsibility (CSR) Initiatives and annual action plan;
d. Performance on Health, Safety and Environment matters at the various manufacturing sites;
e. Overview on Corporate Governance & stakeholder engagements;
f. Employee relations – workforce management and Learning and Development – functional capability building;
g. Enterprise risk management – covering risk relating to Refining & Marketing, Petrochemicals, E&P, new energy businesses and treasury function; 
h. Cyber security and data privacy including emerging cyber security threats
i. Industry outlook and global business scenario;
j. Exploration & Production (E&P) landscape.
Principles covered: All NGRBC Principles
